a5a37dcbc7802166c397899607b721510","tid":948413,"uid":57214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟殺埋身！支那自今年8月首次證實遼寧爆發豬瘟後，疫情在全國蔓延，連鄰近香港的廣東省昨亦淪陷，珠海香洲區一家屠宰場昨確診非洲豬瘟疫情，附近區域全面封鎖，同時來自湖南等的四家供港豬場亦暫停豬隻供港。《蘋果》記者昨晚直擊涉事珠海豬瘟屠宰場，據稱病死豬來自佛山高明。有防疫人員透露，周日已發現死豬，周一開始停運停售，當局昨才通報疫情，被指有遲報疫情之嫌。香港業界擔憂疫情若持續爆發，將影響供應，供港豬肉價格恐會上漲。"},{"pid":"cb85c444816b1596d4d658d8cb01513a4d2751f0","tid":948413,"uid":60187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78dace374cc35fe11f5e7b0c9eb7226af605e495","tid":948413,"uid":206224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f97991d642eba241bdc2d794a6b80b24fd844b01","tid":948413,"uid":129378,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"要買就買外國豬肉，價錢唔係貴好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"丹麥豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"新界豬"},{"pid":"7e9369763a07062fa457e1f8a3117b47039ac6a6","tid":948413,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c2dadf22c83eca67ad62b3b4f11bc20e79798b","tid":948413,"uid":18479,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 荒謬<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a9daab4315b09cd4a2d38351a7d467e177ecc1","tid":948413,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"聖誕買隻火雞返黎食半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11626a2836a1d26935b0e998699a2bbe